snippet.title: Mul-Ty-Player 1.3
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Ty the Tasmanian Tiger Multiplayer mod.
This project is the culmination of the last 4 months of my life.

This is just the beginning and I can't wait to take this even further.
For Christmas however, I thought I'd try to get a full stable release out publicly so everyone else in the community or just interested in the game can give it a go with a friend.
https://github.com/xMcacutt/Mul-Ty-Player
Instructions to install are available on the project GitHub page.

Have fun and Merry Christmas :)
